00:38:33.010 --> 00:38:36.190
And I'm talking to some
women at MIT about,

00:38:36.190 --> 00:38:40.490
perhaps, doing some #metoo
stories at MIT and beyond,

00:38:40.490 --> 00:38:42.400
but we'll have to see.

00:38:42.400 --> 00:38:44.200
I'm suddenly very
intrigued by the idea--

00:38:44.200 --> 00:38:47.980
the role that this kind of
photography and storytelling

00:38:47.980 --> 00:38:51.670
can play in changing
people's attitudes.

00:38:51.670 --> 00:38:53.152
AUDIENCE: Thank
you for your talk.

00:38:53.152 --> 00:38:53.860
I had a question.

00:38:53.860 --> 00:38:57.040
You gave this book out to a
