00:39:04.960 --> 00:39:09.400
increased freedom and peer
mentorship in the following

00:39:09.400 --> 00:39:13.030
years when that class went on
to be sophomores and juniors?

00:39:13.030 --> 00:39:15.940
Did they carry that on back
to the new incoming freshmen?

00:39:15.940 --> 00:39:16.270
DANIEL JACKSON: That's
a great question.

00:39:16.270 --> 00:39:19.420
And it was only last year, so
