00:39:21.010 --> 00:39:22.750
interested in tracking that.

00:39:22.750 --> 00:39:27.430
I'm not sure how this
particular intervention would

00:39:27.430 --> 00:39:30.070
be decoupled from other ones.

00:39:30.070 --> 00:39:34.570
I do have some anecdotal
reactions, a couple of cases

00:39:34.570 --> 00:39:38.650
where students have sent very
